     7‚Üí## TypeScript v5
     9‚ÜíBecause it relies on [const type parameters](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/release-notes/typescript-5-0.html#const-type-parameters), TS-Pattern v5 requires TypeScript v5+!
    10‚Üí
    65‚Üí## chainable methods
    67‚ÜíTS-Pattern v5's major addition is the ability to chain methods to narrow down the values matched by primitive patterns, like `P.string` or `P.number`.
    68‚Üí
    69‚ÜíSince a few examples is worth a thousand words, here are a few ways you can use chainable methods:
    70‚Üí
